Feline::
She wastched Chordate runn off down the hall. "Bye Dreambot."  she 
smiled and sighed a bit.  She stood in the hall where Chordate had 
left her.  She turned and walked down the hall in the opposite 
direction that Chordate ran. She had a sweet smile on her face and 
looked around, mapping out the ship as she went.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DarkMouse::
She looked up at Quickstrike."Forgive me comander, I failed you," she 
whipsered.  She still shook a bit under the pelt, but was slowly 
feeling warmer.  And the shaking was settling down.  She smiled a 
little bit more as she slowly regained control of her body. "But it 
is good to see you again commander."
